'''阿扎瓦德民族解放运动'''（{{lang-ar|الحركة الوطنية لتحرير أزواد}}，{{lang-fr|Mouvement National pour la Libération de l'Azawad}}，簡稱'''MNLA'''），以前的名称是'''阿扎瓦德民族运动'''<Ref name="Africa"/>（{{lang-fr|Mouvement national de l'Azawad}}，簡稱'''MNA'''）是活动于[[马里|马里]][[阿扎瓦德|阿扎瓦德地区]]一个政治军事组织。该组织据说由[[图阿雷格人|图阿雷格人]]组成，曾经协助利比亚政府军作战<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hMSOBkx7DTl29wj-3y5u-439CxXw?docId=80cfb271010b4a499761b797dc31eb62|title=Tuareg rebels attack 6th town in Mali|date=2012-01-31|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work=Google News|last=Vogl|first=Martin|accessdate=2012-02-04}}</ref>，但是一些图阿雷格人站在利比亚[[全国过渡委员会|全国过渡委员会]]一边。利比亚内战于2011年10月结束后，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动随即宣布成立，并包含其他撒哈拉部落人。马里政府指控该组织与[[伊斯兰马格里布基地组织|伊斯兰马格里布基地组织]]有联系<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/mali-government-official-says-al-qaida-fighters-among-those-attacking-northern-towns/2012/01/27/gIQANfYCVQ_story.html|title=Mali government official says al-Qaida fighters among those attacking northern towns|date=2012-01-27|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|work=washingtonpost.com|accessdate=2012-02-04|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605142828/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/mali-government-official-says-al-qaida-fighters-among-those-attacking-northern-towns/2012/01/27/gIQANfYCVQ_story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但是MNLA否认这一指控。

==历史==
[[Image:Azawad_in_context.JPG|thumb]]
从1916年（那时候是法属殖民地时期）以来，至少有5次图阿雷格叛乱。2011年卡扎菲政府被推翻后，在利比亚政府军中的一些图阿雷格人转移到马里北部。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://allafrica.com/stories/201201200939.html|title=Mali: 47 Die in Clashes Between Troops, Rebels - Ministry|date=2012-01-19|work=allafrica.com|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123082213/http://allafrica.com/stories/201201200939.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>这些军事人员与马里北方图阿雷格运动（Northern Mali Tuareg Movement）融合，组建了阿扎瓦德民族解放运动。由于利比亚内战及战后利比亚国内混乱局势，大量重武器、弹药流散到撒哈拉部落地区。<ref name="magharebia">{{cite news|url=http://www.magharebia.com/cocoon/awi/xhtml1/en_GB/features/awi/features/2012/01/30/feature-01|title=Loose Libyan missiles threaten air traffic|date=2012-01-30|last1=Oumar|first1=Jemal|last2=Ramzi|first2=Walid|work=Magharebia|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120131025157/http://www.magharebia.com/cocoon/awi/xhtml1/en_GB/features/awi/features/2012/01/30/feature-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="1source"/>这大大加强了图阿雷格人的军事实力。<ref name="Africa">{{cite news|url=http://thinkafricapress.com/mali/causes-uprising-northern-mali-tuareg|title=The Causes of the Uprising in Northern Mali|date=2012-02-06|last=Morgan|first=Andy|publisher=Think Africa Press|accessdate=2012-02-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310211808/http://thinkafricapress.com/mali/causes-uprising-northern-mali-tuareg|archivedate=2012-03-10}}</ref>

[[File:MNLA_flag.svg|thumb]]
马里政府指控阿扎瓦德民族解放运动与伊斯兰马格里布基地组织有联系<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/mali-government-official-says-al-qaida-fighters-among-those-attacking-northern-towns/2012/01/27/gIQANfYCVQ_story.html|title=Mali government official says al-Qaida fighters among those attacking northern towns|date=2012-01-27|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2012-02-04|archive-date=2019-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605142828/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/africa/mali-government-official-says-al-qaida-fighters-among-those-attacking-northern-towns/2012/01/27/gIQANfYCVQ_story.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，但阿扎瓦德民族解放运动否认这一指控<ref>{{cite news|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/topNews/idAFJOE80Q0AW20120127|title=Mali says rebels fight with Qaeda, rebels deny|date=2012-01-27|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|work=Reuters Africa|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203050134/http://af.reuters.com/article/topNews/idAFJOE80Q0AW20120127|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

阿扎瓦德民族解放运动组建于2011年10月。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/ap/article/ALeqM5hJpQPmk10FgL-18kQKNxds59_VUg?docId=8ed20fbed5254a03b250f00f52b0682d|title=In Mali, a Tuareg rebellion _ without Gadhafi|date=2012-01-26|last=Vogl|first=Martin|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|work=Google News|accessdate=2012-02-05}}{{Dead link}}</ref>但其前身据说建立时间要早近一年。<ref name="eur">{{cite news|url=http://www.eurasiareview.com/20012012-mali-fighting-in-north-the-new-touareg-war/|title=Mali: Fighting In North; The New Touareg War|date=2012-01-20|publisher=Eurasia Review|accessdate=2012-02-10|archive-date=2013-07-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IIzECzYp?url=http://www.eurasiareview.com/20012012-mali-fighting-in-north-the-new-touareg-war/|dead-url=no}}</ref>相較於其他有關組織，MNLA把自己定位解放所有阿扎瓦德人民（[[桑海人|桑海人]]、[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]、[[富拉尼人|富拉尼人]]和[[圖阿雷格人|圖阿雷格人]]）的運動。<Ref name="Africa"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mnlamov.net/english/101-they-are-not-mercenaries.html|title=They are not mercenaries|date=2012-01-22|work=mnlamov.net|accessdate=2012-02-10|archive-date=2012-09-16|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6AiDwGXzx?url=http://www.mnlamov.net/english/101-they-are-not-mercenaries.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==独立战争==
阿扎瓦德民族解放运动在2012年1月开始了武装军事斗争<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.janes.com/products/janes/defence-security-report.aspx?ID=1065932249&channel=security|title=JTIC Brief: MNLA re-awakens Tuareg separatism in Mali|date=2012-02-02|publisher=[[Jane's_Information_Group|Jane's Information Group]]|accessdate=2012-02-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121208220008/http://www.janes.com/products/janes/defence-security-report.aspx?ID=1065932249&channel=security|archivedate=2012-12-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-16643507|title=Dozens of Tuareg rebels dead in Mali clash, says army|date=2012-01-20|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=2012-02-04|archive-date=2021-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423112532/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-16643507|dead-url=no}}</ref>，目的是要解放在政府控制下的三个半[[大区|大区]]<ref name="1source"/>以赢得阿扎瓦德的独立。<ref name="reuters"/>
[[File:Northern_Mali_conflict.svg|thumb]]

在2012年1月，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动攻占了昂代郎布坎（Andéramboukane）、梅纳卡（Menaka）、泰萨利特（Tessalit）、尼亚丰凯（Niafunké）、阿盖洛克（Aguelhoc）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stratfor.com/weekly/mali-besieged-fighters-fleeing-libya|title=Mali Besieged by Fighters Fleeing Libya|date=2012-02-02|last=Stewart|first=Scott|publisher=[[Stratfor|Stratfor]]|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311024311/http://www.stratfor.com/weekly/mali-besieged-fighters-fleeing-libya|archive-date=2012-03-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，控制了马里北方部分地区。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5iVW1DBI8ZiwzUAkN8MSZ9Mgpcx-Q?docId=CNG.028f1f77f56e33c1084cdd34a97858f3.471|title=Tuareg rebels take Mali town after army pullout|date=2012-02-01|agency=Agence France-Presse|work=Google News|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2013-01-03|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130103173726/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5iVW1DBI8ZiwzUAkN8MSZ9Mgpcx-Q?docId=CNG.028f1f77f56e33c1084cdd34a97858f3.471|dead-url=no}}</ref>还攻占了马里第5大城镇莱雷（Léré）。<ref name="AJ120126">{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2012/01/201212614823523986.html|title=Tuareg rebels attack fifth town in Mali|date=2012-01-26|work=[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-11-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6COdVcaGP?url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/africa/2012/01/201212614823523986.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2012年1月，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动宣布击落一架马里空军的[[米格-21|米格-21]]战斗机，使用的是北约空投给利比亚反卡扎菲军事力量的[[地对空导弹|地对空导弹]]。<ref name="magharebia"/>马里空军也使用了[[米-24|米-24]]“雌鹿”或[[直-9|直-9]]“海豚”武装直升机用机炮对地轰击。<ref name="eur"/>2月4日，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动攻击了马里最东北部的大区首府基达尔(Kidal)，意图占领该城镇，控制那里的两个军事基地。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E8D400420120204|title=Heavy weapons fire rocks town in Mali's north|date=2012-02-04|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|work=Reuters Africa|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-11-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6COe3xyBF?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/04/mali-rebels-attack-idAFL5E8D400420120204|dead-url=yes}}</ref>同时，在马里南部政府控制区[[巴马科|巴马科]]的图阿雷格人因此担心遭到报复而开始撤离。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E8D27OC20120202|title=UPDATE 1-Mali capital paralysed by anti-rebellion protests|date=2012-02-02|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|work=Reuters Africa|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222084028/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFL5E8D27OC20120202|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[国际红十字委员会|国际红十字委员会]]说3,500人逃入[[毛里塔尼亚|毛里塔尼亚]]，10,000人逃入[[尼日尔|尼日尔]]以躲避战乱。<ref name="reuters">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/05/us-mali-rebels-attack-idUSTRE8130H920120205|title=Mali says 20 rebels killed, thousands flee|date=2012-02-04|last1=Diallo|first1=Tiemoko|last2=Diarra|first2=Adama|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205102513/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/05/us-mali-rebels-attack-idUSTRE8130H920120205|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2月8日，马里政府军放弃了在阿尔及利亚边境上的城镇廷扎瓦滕（Tinzaouaten），在此前战斗中政府军阵亡1人、负伤2人，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动也有1人阵亡、1人受伤，但控制该地后虏获了两个军事基地存储的武器弹药。联合国宣布有超过20000人逃到了邻国[[布基纳法索|布基纳法索]]、毛里塔尼亚、尼日尔，并警告由于战乱将导致食品短缺。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/maliNews/idAFL5E8D8A0G20120209|title=UPDATE 1-Malian rebels seize key border town, civilians flee|date=2012-02-09|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|accessdate=2012-02-10|archive-date=2012-11-23|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6COeMVSlO?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/02/09/mali-rebels-town-idAFL5E8D8A0G20120209|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 总计有100000人流离失所成为难民，至少四分之一进入尼日尔。{{fact|date=February 2012}}<!--from al jazeera-->[[西非国家经济共同体|西非国家经济共同体]]计划派遣暴力冲突调查组，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/english/news/africa/ECOWAS-Team-to-Investigate-Fighting-in-Mali--138982439.html|title=ECOWAS Team to Investigate Fighting in Mali|date=2012-02-08|last=Clottey|first=Peter|publisher=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]]|accessdate=2012-02-09}}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>并谴责暴力行动、号召对马里政府提供后勤支援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/regions/africa/120320/mali-news-ecowas-warns-tuareg-rebels |title=存档副本 |access-date=2012-03-22 |archive-date=2012-11-24 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6CPBgoy7Y?url=http://www.globalpost.com/dispatch/news/regions/africa/120320/mali-news-ecowas-warns-tuareg-rebels |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2012年4月6日，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动宣布独立战争胜利结束，阿扎瓦德独立<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mnlamov.net/component/content/article/169-declaration-dindependance-de-lazawad.html|title=DÉCLARATION D’INDÉPENDANCE DE L'AZAWAD|date=2012-04-06|accessdate=2012-04-07|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BTul59wU?url=http://www.mnlamov.net/component/content/article/169-declaration-dindependance-de-lazawad.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年5月26日，阿扎瓦德民族解放運動與伊斯蘭武裝組織[[伊斯蘭衛士|伊斯蘭衛士]]宣佈達成合併協議，建立一個伊斯蘭國家。<ref name=BBC265>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-18224004 |title=Mali Tuareg and Islamist rebels agree on Sharia state |date=2012-05-26 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2012-05-27 |archive-date=2013-07-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IIzGePzG?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-18224004 |dead-url=no }}</ref>稍後有報道指阿扎瓦德民族解放運動決定退出協議，與伊斯蘭衛士保持距離。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.fasozine.com/index.php/le-blog-de-barkbiiga/le-blog-de-barkbiiga/8518-nord-mali-le-mnla-refuse-de-se-mettre-len-sardiner|agency=FasoZine|title=Nord Mali: le MNLA refuse de se mettre "en sardine"!|first=Bark|last=Biiga|date=2012-06-03|accessdate=2012-06-03|language=fr|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120608054030/http://www.fasozine.com/index.php/le-blog-de-barkbiiga/le-blog-de-barkbiiga/8518-nord-mali-le-mnla-refuse-de-se-mettre-len-sardiner|archivedate=2012-06-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/content/mali-islamists-reopen-talks-with-tuareg-rebels/1146352.html|agency=Voice of America|title=Mali Islamists Reopen Talks With Tuareg Rebels|date=2012-06-02|accessdate=2012-06-02|archive-date=2012-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604000632/http://www.voanews.com/content/mali-islamists-reopen-talks-with-tuareg-rebels/1146352.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>雙方持續衝突，<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-18377168|title = Mali rebel groups 'clash in Kidal'|date = 2012-06-08|publisher = BBC News|access-date = 2013-01-15|archive-date = 2012-12-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121223052848/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-africa-18377168|dead-url = no}}</ref>在6月的[[加奧|加奧]]之戰，伊斯蘭衛士與[[西非聖戰統一運動|西非聖戰統一運動]]合力擊敗阿扎瓦德民族解放運動，伊斯蘭衛士隨後宣佈控制了馬里北方所有城市。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/28/us-mali-crisis-idUSBRE85R15720120628 |title=Islamists declare full control of Mali's north |author=Tiemoko Diallo and Adama Diarra |date=2012-06-28 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2012-06-29 |archive-date=2013-07-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IIztFRqr?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/06/28/us-mali-crisis-idUSBRE85R15720120628 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==领导层==
创立时的一位领导人是Moussa Ag Acharatoumane<ref name="AJ120126" />。该组织另一位有影响力的领导人是Ibrahim Ag Bahanga（其岳父Hama Ag Sid-{’}-Ahmed是该地区以前叛乱组织的发言人），但于2011年8月26日死亡于利比亚。该组织军事领导人是Ag Mohamed Najem上校<ref name="Africa"/><ref name="eur"/>，是马里本地图阿雷格人。<ref name="1source">{{cite news|url=http://www.thecuttingedgenews.com/index.php?article=71898&pageid=20&pagename=Security|title=Returning Malian Mercenaries Present a Challenge for Mali and the West|date=2012-02-02|last=Stewart|first=Scott|work=[[The_Cutting_Edge_News|The Cutting Edge News]]|accessdate=2012-02-05|archive-date=2012-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601230850/http://www.thecuttingedgenews.com/index.php?article=71898&pageid=20&pagename=Security|dead-url=no}}</ref>该组织大约有40位军官<ref name="Africa"/>，阿扎瓦德民族解放运动总书记是Bilal Ag Cherif<ref name="eur"/>，发言人是Hama Ag Sid'Ahmed，居住在欧洲<ref name="reuters"/>。

